Q: Can you recommend a reputable tour operator in Mumbai? - Eileen NurseA: It is impossible for me to recommend one company but of course there are numerous operators in a city as popular as Mumbai. As always, check out the Internet.Grand Mumbai Tours are top rated on Trip Advisor and won that site's Certificate of Excellence for best guided customised private tours for three years in a row, up to last year. They offer cultural, sightseeing and nightlife tours, and will customise them depending on your interests. Do you have a query for our travel expert? Send your question through to travelmag@sundaytimes.co.za